item.dc:creator: @Aftermath.v2 Aftermath.v2
item.description:
@Aftermath.v2 wrote:

That just clicks in the same spot over and over. Here, this will actually click on the images.

[scar]program RinkRunner;
//http://neopets.com/games/rinkrunner.phtml
//Aftermath.v2
//BETA

var BlackNote: integer;
var GreenNote: integer;
var BlueNote: integer;
var OrangeNote: integer;
var RedNote: integer;

procedure GoButton;
begin
ClickMouse(470, 375, True);
end;

procedure NextButton;
begin
ClickMouse(279, 331, True);
end;

procedure LoadNotes;
begin
BlackNote := DTMFromString(‘78DA630C60646058C4801530C2E830206B060’ +
‘1354140D612026A88B12B14C89A895F0D00F2BF04C6’);
GreenNote := DTMFromString(‘78DA63FCC2C0C0B08B01159C81508C502EE30’ +
‘F20B196809ACF40623B0135BF883467277E3500CAE80C57’);
BlueNote := DTMFromString(‘78DA63FCC3C0C010CC800A66FE07538C502E2’ +
‘32390E54140CD3F22CC21D62E4FFC6A00B6570C87’);
OrangeNote := DTMFromString(‘78DA633CCBC0C0D0CAC8800CFECF84D03051C’ +
‘60B40A28A809A3340A29D0873AA09A8390D24DAF0AB0100730D0E’ +
‘93’);
RedNote := DTMFromString(‘78DA631461646008614001FFA134238C9604B’ +
‘23C09A81105B28208A81103B28209A89102B23CF0AB01008BB807’ +
‘07’);
end;

procedure ClickNote(Note: integer);
var NoteX: integer;
var NoteY: integer;
begin
if( FindDTM(Note, NoteX, NoteY, 0, 0, 550, 400) ) then
ClickMouse(NoteX, NoteY, True);
end;

begin
LoadNotes;
ActivateClient;

Wait(2000);

GoButton;

//Main Loop

repeat

ClickNote(BlackNote);
ClickNote(GreenNote);
ClickNote(BlueNote);
ClickNote(OrangeNote);
ClickNote(RedNote);
NextButton;

until false;

end.[/scar]
